## Description {#details}

<code>llvm.global&#95;ctors</code> and <code>llvm.global&#95;dtors</code> are arrays of <a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/asmprinter/structor">Structor</a> structs.

Priority - init priority Func - global initialization or global clean-up function ComdatKey - associated data
